## Summary

Add the first deterministic automation layer for PULSEmech adoption: a
read-only integration planner that converts a small declared request into a
complete, digest-bound, machine-readable target-repository plan.

The objective is not to reduce PULSEmech complexity.

The objective is to transfer mechanical adoption work from the human operator
to the machine.

```text
target repository
+ declared integration request
+ canonical component manifest
→ dependency-closure resolution
→ policy-derived gate-set materialization
→ target-state inspection
→ deterministic integration plan
```

